# I have successfully harvested another 10 units of iron ore, bringing my total to 10 iron ore in my inventory.
# 
# Now that I have iron ore again, I can return to the furnace and attempt to insert the iron ore for smelting once more.

# Moving back to the furnace position to insert the iron ore.
move_to(Position(x=0.0, y=0.0))  # Moving to the furnace at (0.0, 0.0).
insert_item(Prototype.IronOre, furnace, quantity=10)  # Inserting all 10 iron ore into the furnace.
print(f"Inventory updated to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Displaying updated inventory after insertion.
print(f"Entities on the map: {get_entities()}")  # Displaying the current state of entities on the map.
